cc:Work.dc:title: vCardTools Class Diagram a/o milestone 0.9.3
cc:Work.dc:description: A diagram describing relationships between the PropertySpecification class and the PropertyBuilder/Property interfaces in the vCardTools PHP package (https://github.com/evought/VCard-Tools) a/o Milestone 0.9.3 (pre-release). Describes the refactoring of Properties as first-class types and the resulting VCard structure.
